REPZ




^Ichain instruction




Repeat following CMPSB, CMPSW, SCASB, SCASW instructions
while ZF = 1 (result is Zero), maximum CX times.
Algorithm:

check_cx:
if CX &lt;> 0 then

^Ido following chain instruction
^ICX = CX - 1
^Iif ZF = 1 then:
^I^I
^I^Igo back to check_cx
^I^I
^Ielse
^I^I
^I^Iexit from REPZ cycle
^I^I
^I

else

^Iexit from REPZ cycle







